title: NOAA, High winds reported in parts of U.S. during severe weather event, 22-24 April 2010, USA
name: NOAA, High winds reported in parts of U.S. during severe weather event, 22-24 April 2010, USA
description:
The point shapefile shows locations of high winds reported over the last 72 hours due to a severe weather system affecting parts of Colorado, Texas, Oklahoma, Alabama, Arkansas,Georgia, Kentucky, Tennessee, Illinois.

Look elsewhere on Finder! for more up-to-date reports as well data for tornadoes and highwinds. Use key words: "Severe weather", Hail, Highwind, tornado
